1 elec tee appearing on the first drawn paper shall be declared the
2 winner. The secretary shall then expose the other name or names not
3 drawn to all witnesses present; and
4 5. The meeting shall be held on a weekday, holidays excepted,
5 between the hours of 7:00 a.m. and 7:00 p.m.
6 C. D. When there are three (3) or more candidates and a tie for
7 first place occurs for the nomination of a candidate at a Primary
8 Election for which a Runoff Primary will be held, the names of the
9 tied candidates shall be placed on the Runoff Primary ballot.
10 SECTION 2. This act shall become effective November 1, 2025.
